386→                        <div id="content">Let $k\geq 2$. Is it true that, for any distinct integers $1&#60;n_1&#60;\cdots &#60;n_k$ such that\[1=\frac{1}{n_1}+\cdots+\frac{1}{n_k}\]we must have $\max(n_{i+1}-n_i)\geq 3$?</div>
